description: Variation of Condition 1 (Development in accordance with approved plans) of planning permission reference No. 2012/3693 dated 10 May 2013 to provide a revised mix of accommodation (16 X studio, 156 X 1-bed, 142 X 2-bed and 87 X 3-bed) and revisions to unit sizes and layouts, reductions and increases in private amenity spaces to flats, increase in height and massing of the 31-storey tower (Block 1A), extension to 8th storey of Block 1A, additions and extensions to 5th, 6th, 7th, 8th, 9th & 10th storey of Block 2, redesign of elevations to Blocks 1A, 1B & 2 including altered entrances and materials, and a reduction in the size of the basement.
